data.description: Welcome to charming and peaceful Dunedin! Do you miss your basement but ready for the Florida lifestyle? Look no further! Your new home is a unique split level home offering comfort, privacy and space for the entire family! Through the front door, you will enter into your new living room with coat closet and kitchen featuring ample storage and a pass through to your dining room space, making entertaining a breeze. You then have the choice to go upstairs or downstairs. Upstairs features a large master bedroom as well as ample sized guest bedrooms and pristine bathroom. In the downstairs, there is an additional space that could be used as an additional living space, gym, plenty of room for a pool table, playroom or even extra sleeping space. Your large laundry room, second full bathroom, garage, and entrance to outdoor lanai is through the downstairs space. The backyard is cleared and spacious and is a great spot to host parties or would be excellent to build your new beautiful pool! Solar panels are owned and paid off, saving you on your monthly electric bill! 74 Palm was one of the first built in the neighborhood and has only had a few owners over its lifetime.  Surrounded by $1million+ homes and more being built, live the life of luxury without the luxury price tag! The home has been consistently cared for by its previous owners and now it's time for you to enjoy Dunedin! Located less than 1/2 mile to Dunedin Golf Club, 2 miles to dog friendly downtown Dunedin with tons of shopping, dining and breweries and less than 3 miles to beautiful Honeymoon Island State Park. Mease Dunedin Hospital, and several spring training ball stadiums are also nearby, less than 10 miles to Clearwater Marine Aquarium!
